505
00:34:46,337 --> 00:34:49,507
I'm so grateful
for your support.

506
00:34:52,760 --> 00:34:55,304
I just feel so alone.

507
00:34:56,138 --> 00:34:57,932
You're not alone.

508
00:34:59,266 --> 00:35:00,309
You're not.

509
00:36:16,552 --> 00:36:19,012
I'm not about to
presume what you know

