00:36:25,686 --> 00:36:28,062
with a plan to kill Betty Gore.

513
00:36:28,063 --> 00:36:31,441
She didn't cook her kids breakfast,
head off to Bible school,

514
00:36:31,442 --> 00:36:33,735
perform a parable
in the sanctuary,

515
00:36:33,736 --> 00:36:36,946
drive out to Wylie to pick up
Alisa's swimsuit, and then say,

516
00:36:36,947 --> 00:36:40,659
"Hey, while I'm at it, let's
