517
00:36:41,660 --> 00:36:43,870
That makes zero sense.

518
00:36:43,871 --> 00:36:45,206
Zero.

519
00:36:45,956 --> 00:36:49,209
What happened here is not just
the most plausible scenario.

520
00:36:49,210 --> 00:36:52,045
It's also exactly
