00:46:17,194 --> 00:46:18,434
But I'm sure lucky to have you.

676
00:46:21,991 --> 00:46:22,991
We're both lucky.

677
00:46:27,121 --> 00:46:28,872
I think I wanna go back
and wait it out with Don

678
00:46:28,873 --> 00:46:31,916
'cause I just am feeling a
little too anxious sittin' here.

