00:48:10,266 --> 00:48:13,394
And now don't think I'm picking
on y'all. That's standard.

695
00:48:14,395 --> 00:48:15,475
Alright, bring the jury in.

696
00:48:26,615 --> 00:48:27,615
Be seated.

